			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Contrary to popular belief, this is a truly wonderful spell! From a pessimistic point of view, it does have a short duration when you first get it, and it only does about 6 damage per hit. But as you advance, you will learn the potential of this spell, for 40 mana, it can do well over 100 damage in a battle,and its duration will increase, giving you time to meditate and get that mana back. And if you are really observant and experimental, you will see that it also adds a nifty +10 bonus to the recipient's Save vs. heat(of fire, whatever). Trust me, you will have this spell memorized all the way to level 20(when you get a better one :P).<BR>
<BR>
~Athas~<BR>
Magician of the 17th circle<BR>
